---
import Section from "./ui/section.astro";
import Container from "./ui/container.astro";
---

<Section class="bg-bg-card border-y border-border" noContainer>
    <div
        class="absolute top-10 left-10 font-serif text-[150px] leading-none text-primary/5 pointer-events-none select-none"
    >
        "
    </div>

    <Container className="relative z-10 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <p
                class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-4xl italic leading-relaxed text-text-main mb-12"
            >
                "Consigo anunciar com tranquilidade, pois tenho total certeza de
                que todo o lead vai ver o site instantaneamente! E sempre que
                precisei do suporte ele foi instantâneo"
            </p>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-bg-elevated rounded-full border border-border flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-primary text-xl"
                >
                    JL
                </div>
                <div class="text-left">
                    <div class="font-bold text-white">Julio Leite</div>
                    <div
                        class="text-sm text-primary uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold"
                    >
                        Pórtico Reformas
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</Section>
